Bushfire warning level: ADVICE
Queensland Fire and Emergency Services (QFES) advises there is a bushfire in Springbrook.

Currently as at 5.45pm Friday 28 August a bushfire is burning west of the Springbrook Road and Pine Creek Road intersection in Springbrook. Firefighters will continue backburning throughout the night near Springbrook Road. Traffic restrictions continue along Springbrook Road near Pine Creek Road and motorists should drive with caution and to conditions.
